WEBVTT

00:00:01.105 --> 00:00:03.425
This place isn't just about drugs.

00:00:03.505 --> 00:00:05.985
They also run illegal boxing matches.

00:00:06.065 --> 00:00:08.985
The operation is led by Yu
from the Special Investigation Unit.

00:00:11.745 --> 00:00:13.025
I'm Yu.

00:00:13.105 --> 00:00:15.225
This is Lee.
We're from the Special Investigation Unit.

00:00:15.305 --> 00:00:16.545
Wasn't it you

00:00:16.625 --> 00:00:19.305
who sold Puifai's clip to Time
in exchange for money?

00:00:21.945 --> 00:00:23.185
Do you want to bet?

00:00:23.785 --> 00:00:26.585
If my guy loses, I'll resign.

00:00:34.225 --> 00:00:35.465
What's up, Jay?

00:00:35.545 --> 00:00:36.785
Where are you, Tonkla?

00:00:37.905 --> 00:00:39.905
I'm at the garage. What's up?

00:00:40.545 --> 00:00:41.785
Can I come over?

00:00:48.745 --> 00:00:50.305
Kla!

00:01:43.905 --> 00:01:45.465
He's huge.

00:01:45.545 --> 00:01:46.785
Are you sure he can handle him?

00:01:48.865 --> 00:01:51.105
I trust Jade's skills. He'll be fine.

00:02:01.505 --> 00:02:02.585
Is that all you've got?

00:02:03.185 --> 00:02:05.225
Fine. I'll handle it, asshole!

00:02:32.185 --> 00:02:33.225
Let's have some fun.

00:02:34.105 --> 00:02:36.305
I'm already having fun.

00:02:45.145 --> 00:02:46.145
You're dead, you bastard!

00:03:05.945 --> 00:03:07.425
Just give up, you piece of shit!

00:03:10.265 --> 00:03:11.225
Go help Kamin first!

00:03:37.145 --> 00:03:38.225
Jade!

00:03:38.305 --> 00:03:40.545
Honestly, your guy is skilled.

00:03:40.625 --> 00:03:42.225
He just lacks experience.

00:03:44.985 --> 00:03:48.065
If you hadn't played dirty,
my guy would've won anyway.

00:03:49.105 --> 00:03:50.345
Too bad.

00:03:50.425 --> 00:03:52.425
There were never any rules here
to begin with.

00:03:59.905 --> 00:04:02.945
It looks like you finally understand
what "no rules" means, Inspector.

00:04:03.025 --> 00:04:04.985
You played dirty on my guy first.

00:04:05.065 --> 00:04:06.185
I won't let this slide.

00:04:06.265 --> 00:04:07.785
Even if you shoot me,

00:04:09.025 --> 00:04:10.705
you're not getting out of here.

00:04:12.345 --> 00:04:14.945
That jerk, Jade,
is just one of your subordinates.

00:04:15.545 --> 00:04:18.225
Do you think it's even worth it
to trade your life for him?

00:04:18.305 --> 00:04:19.425
Worth it.

00:04:19.504 --> 00:04:21.064
He's more than just a subordinate.

00:04:21.705 --> 00:04:24.625
And don't ever call my people jerks!

00:04:27.105 --> 00:04:28.705
Since our deal's off,

00:04:29.425 --> 00:04:32.145
I'll excuse myself, Inspector.

00:04:50.585 --> 00:04:51.705
Hey, you fucking asshole!

00:04:54.025 --> 00:04:56.185
Jade, don't be pathetic.

00:04:56.265 --> 00:04:57.145
Get a grip!

00:05:54.145 --> 00:05:55.465
Stand down, everyone!

00:05:55.545 --> 00:05:57.105
Stand down, everyone!

00:05:57.745 --> 00:05:59.905
- Stand down, everyone!
- Police officer! Don't move!

00:06:01.665 --> 00:06:02.745
- Sit down!
- Jade.

00:06:02.825 --> 00:06:05.185
Jade, are you okay?

00:06:06.385 --> 00:06:07.785
Where's Kamin?

00:06:07.865 --> 00:06:09.065
Get up first.

00:06:09.145 --> 00:06:10.985
I heard a gunshot. Where's Kamin?

00:06:16.465 --> 00:06:17.585
I'm here.

00:06:37.265 --> 00:06:38.385
Hold on.

00:06:39.745 --> 00:06:41.105
- Give me a second.
- Sit down first.

00:06:51.425 --> 00:06:52.385
Does it hurt badly?

00:06:54.705 --> 00:06:55.905
Not…

00:06:57.945 --> 00:06:58.865
really.

00:07:01.425 --> 00:07:02.625
I just want a little pampering.

00:07:03.465 --> 00:07:04.345
Really?

00:07:04.425 --> 00:07:05.425
Hey!

00:07:06.025 --> 00:07:07.225
What are you doing?

00:07:08.105 --> 00:07:09.185
That hurts.

00:07:09.705 --> 00:07:11.585
You just said you're tough earlier.

00:07:12.865 --> 00:07:14.625
You know how sharp my mouth is.

00:07:16.665 --> 00:07:18.185
Or did you forget?

00:07:20.345 --> 00:07:21.585
Take a look at yourself first.

00:07:23.065 --> 00:07:25.145
Look at all those wounds.
You're still acting tough.

00:07:26.865 --> 00:07:28.065
Matching wounds.

00:07:28.905 --> 00:07:30.025
So we match.

00:07:30.825 --> 00:07:33.585
You've got one, so I needed one too.

00:07:33.665 --> 00:07:35.065
They're not matching anymore.

00:07:36.105 --> 00:07:38.065
You've got way more than me now.

00:07:38.145 --> 00:07:40.025
Try being more careful.

00:07:40.865 --> 00:07:42.065
Don't go all in all the time.

00:07:44.625 --> 00:07:46.705
What are you trying to say?

00:07:46.785 --> 00:07:48.185
I'm the only one allowed

00:07:49.785 --> 00:07:51.145
to mess with my subordinate.

00:07:54.745 --> 00:07:59.105
I'll only let you call me that
during work hours.

00:08:00.265 --> 00:08:01.545
Once we're home,

00:08:02.665 --> 00:08:03.745
I'll call you something else.

00:08:06.625 --> 00:08:08.385
And since I won today,

00:08:09.105 --> 00:08:11.465
keep your promise.

00:08:24.985 --> 00:08:26.145
I don't break promises.

00:08:52.545 --> 00:08:53.945
Hey.

00:08:54.025 --> 00:08:55.185
Inspector?

00:08:56.825 --> 00:08:57.705
Hey.

00:08:58.305 --> 00:08:59.625
What are you doing?

00:09:03.425 --> 00:09:05.425
I pay the rent,

00:09:05.505 --> 00:09:06.705
so I get the bed.

00:09:06.785 --> 00:09:08.385
If we're sleeping in the same room,

00:09:09.225 --> 00:09:10.665
we share the same bed.

00:09:11.265 --> 00:09:12.945
I said I'd stay in this room,

00:09:13.585 --> 00:09:15.825
not share a bed with you.

00:09:18.465 --> 00:09:21.385
You're getting on my nerves, Inspector.

00:09:28.145 --> 00:09:29.105
Come here.

00:09:30.225 --> 00:09:31.785
I'll be nice since you're hurt.

00:09:32.385 --> 00:09:34.945
Once you're better,
you can go back to the floor.

00:09:37.225 --> 00:09:38.225
How kind of you.

00:09:47.465 --> 00:09:49.625
I know the deal was more than this,

00:09:49.705 --> 00:09:54.025
but you can't even move
or use any strength right now.

00:09:54.745 --> 00:09:56.225
We'll talk once you recover.

00:09:58.785 --> 00:10:02.545
Besides getting on my nerves,
do you like giving people hope?

00:10:09.105 --> 00:10:10.105
Come here.

00:10:15.305 --> 00:10:17.345
If getting hurt gets me this,

00:10:18.145 --> 00:10:19.225
I'd say it was worth it.

00:11:10.905 --> 00:11:12.105
Have you seen Jay?

00:11:12.905 --> 00:11:14.305
He didn't come home last night.

00:11:16.145 --> 00:11:17.225
Not yet.

00:11:20.465 --> 00:11:22.425
No matter how late it is,
he always comes home.

00:11:26.985 --> 00:11:28.025
JAY

00:11:33.065 --> 00:11:36.305
Please leave your number for a callback.

00:11:37.025 --> 00:11:38.105
You can't reach him?

00:11:39.665 --> 00:11:40.865
He's not picking up.

00:11:46.225 --> 00:11:47.185
Hello?

00:11:47.265 --> 00:11:48.465
Tankhun?

00:11:51.545 --> 00:11:52.385
Yes.

00:11:53.385 --> 00:11:54.905
What happened?

00:11:55.865 --> 00:11:56.945
Jay's at the scene.

00:11:57.705 --> 00:11:58.905
Tonkla's dead.

00:12:07.425 --> 00:12:08.905
Take photos here, please.

00:12:15.985 --> 00:12:18.225
What happened to my brother?

00:12:18.305 --> 00:12:19.905
He's still unconscious.
We need to get him to the hospital.

00:12:19.985 --> 00:12:21.745
- Jay!
- Hey.

00:12:22.345 --> 00:12:23.585
Let them take him for examination first.

00:12:24.625 --> 00:12:25.785
Please excuse us.

00:12:30.345 --> 00:12:32.345
Lieutenant, is he a witness?

00:12:33.265 --> 00:12:34.265
What do we know so far?

00:12:34.345 --> 00:12:35.705
This is the garage owner.

00:12:36.745 --> 00:12:37.985
He was the first to find Tonkla's body.

00:12:38.825 --> 00:12:40.785
I opened the garage like usual

00:12:40.865 --> 00:12:43.945
and found the two boys like this,

00:12:44.025 --> 00:12:45.665
so I called the police.

00:12:47.185 --> 00:12:48.425
Please come with me.

00:12:59.265 --> 00:13:00.385
Is something wrong?

00:13:01.385 --> 00:13:04.185
A car that was parked here is gone.

00:13:10.305 --> 00:13:12.505
Maybe a customer came to pick it up.

00:13:16.425 --> 00:13:17.465
Hello, Inspector.

00:13:17.545 --> 00:13:18.865
Hello.

00:13:19.705 --> 00:13:22.825
Don't worry about your brother.

00:13:22.905 --> 00:13:24.945
Based on the initial examination,

00:13:25.025 --> 00:13:29.065
he likely took a heavy blow to the head
and lost consciousness.

00:13:29.145 --> 00:13:32.945
But we'll do an MRI at the hospital
for a more detailed examination.

00:13:33.025 --> 00:13:34.265
Don't worry.

00:13:36.185 --> 00:13:37.385
Please take care of Jay.

00:13:37.465 --> 00:13:38.705
Of course.

00:13:38.785 --> 00:13:41.785
By the way, how did you get his number?

00:13:43.145 --> 00:13:44.905
I don't remember you two
exchanging contacts.

00:13:44.985 --> 00:13:49.065
Well, I got it from
the investigation team.

00:13:49.145 --> 00:13:51.985
I thought he would want updates quickly.

00:13:52.065 --> 00:13:53.865
Getting someone's number
without permission,

00:13:53.945 --> 00:13:56.545
isn't that crossing a line?

00:13:56.625 --> 00:13:58.025
I think you've gone too far.

00:13:58.985 --> 00:14:02.545
I believe Inspector Kamin
is professional enough

00:14:03.385 --> 00:14:04.985
not to take this personally.

00:14:07.905 --> 00:14:09.385
So what do we know now?

00:14:21.465 --> 00:14:23.065
His legs were crushed?

00:14:23.665 --> 00:14:24.665
Yes.

00:14:25.265 --> 00:14:28.025
Based on the time of death
and his injuries,

00:14:28.105 --> 00:14:30.305
his legs were broken first,

00:14:30.385 --> 00:14:31.425
so he couldn't escape.

00:14:31.505 --> 00:14:34.945
Then a heavy object was dropped on him,

00:14:35.025 --> 00:14:36.225
killing him.

00:14:41.545 --> 00:14:42.985
EVIDENCE, DO NOT MOVE

00:14:48.025 --> 00:14:49.305
The real letter is with us.

00:14:50.625 --> 00:14:53.025
The killer left a fake one here.

00:14:54.105 --> 00:14:55.465
What a blatant provocation.

00:15:04.465 --> 00:15:07.625
EVIDENCE, DO NOT MOVE

00:15:29.345 --> 00:15:30.185
Jay.

00:15:31.305 --> 00:15:32.665
Jay, are you okay?

00:15:32.745 --> 00:15:33.665
Hold on.

00:15:33.745 --> 00:15:35.185
Slowly.

00:15:37.505 --> 00:15:39.465
Jade, I'm sorry.

00:15:40.145 --> 00:15:41.345
I'm sorry.

00:15:42.865 --> 00:15:46.265
Tonkla's dead!

00:15:48.585 --> 00:15:49.665
Lie down.

00:15:54.745 --> 00:15:55.825
Slowly.

00:15:58.025 --> 00:15:59.465
Jay, did you see who attacked him?

00:16:00.385 --> 00:16:03.305
No. I don't remember.

00:16:08.825 --> 00:16:09.745
Jay.

00:16:09.825 --> 00:16:11.505
I understand

00:16:13.185 --> 00:16:15.265
you don't want to think
about what happened again.

00:16:18.185 --> 00:16:20.545
But try to think back one more time.

00:16:23.265 --> 00:16:25.065
What was the atmosphere like?

00:16:26.265 --> 00:16:27.705
Sounds,

00:16:27.785 --> 00:16:29.745
smells,

00:16:29.825 --> 00:16:31.225
or anything.

00:16:31.985 --> 00:16:33.785
Can you tell us?

00:16:35.705 --> 00:16:37.425
It will really help the case.

00:16:39.985 --> 00:16:42.145
All I remember is

00:16:42.225 --> 00:16:43.865
when I got to the garage,

00:16:43.945 --> 00:16:46.505
Tonkla was already lying still.

00:16:46.585 --> 00:16:48.385
I also remember

00:16:49.585 --> 00:16:51.865
the attacker was a man.

00:16:53.785 --> 00:16:55.545
But before I saw his face,

00:16:55.625 --> 00:16:59.145
I got hit on the head and blacked out.

00:17:01.625 --> 00:17:02.985
So there was someone else?

00:17:06.825 --> 00:17:08.464
I'm sorry.

00:17:08.545 --> 00:17:11.825
It's okay. I'm just glad you woke up.

00:17:24.184 --> 00:17:26.424
So if someone else hit Jay,

00:17:27.464 --> 00:17:29.145
that means there's another culprit, right?

00:17:31.185 --> 00:17:32.905
Or maybe Jay did it,

00:17:33.665 --> 00:17:34.665
but he is lying.

00:17:36.985 --> 00:17:38.065
Why would you suspect him?

00:17:39.465 --> 00:17:41.665
He was the only one at the scene.

00:17:41.745 --> 00:17:43.465
He can say anything, right?

00:17:43.545 --> 00:17:44.705
Hey.

00:17:45.305 --> 00:17:47.625
I'm not trying to disrespect
your brother or anything,

00:17:48.185 --> 00:17:51.025
but Jay is way out of his depth
when it comes to killing someone.

00:17:51.905 --> 00:17:53.265
He's not ruthless enough.

00:17:53.345 --> 00:17:55.185
Do you really think he could?

00:17:56.825 --> 00:17:58.865
But if he remembers nothing,

00:17:59.465 --> 00:18:01.345
how can he prove he's innocent?

00:18:02.305 --> 00:18:05.025
Right now, it feels like the culprit
is always one step ahead of us.

00:18:05.745 --> 00:18:07.545
They know everything we're about to do.

00:18:09.065 --> 00:18:11.385
That's why I suspect the culprit
might be someone on the inside.

00:18:15.745 --> 00:18:17.065
Here's the thing.

00:18:18.465 --> 00:18:20.025
You can rest assured.

00:18:20.745 --> 00:18:22.225
If Jay remembers anything,

00:18:22.305 --> 00:18:24.065
he'll tell you himself.

00:18:24.145 --> 00:18:25.265
All right?

00:18:27.705 --> 00:18:31.345
What I want you to do is take care of Jay.

00:18:32.185 --> 00:18:33.545
He's lying there, looking helpless.

00:18:34.665 --> 00:18:35.825
Right?

00:18:35.905 --> 00:18:36.825
Don't worry.

00:18:36.905 --> 00:18:39.225
I'll handle the leads.

00:18:39.305 --> 00:18:41.265
I'll talk to the investigation team

00:18:41.345 --> 00:18:43.505
and see if we can get
more leads on the killer.

00:18:46.105 --> 00:18:47.105
No.

00:18:48.225 --> 00:18:50.065
I can separate work from personal matters.

00:18:53.065 --> 00:18:55.105
When we raided Seon Jae's nest last night,

00:18:55.185 --> 00:18:56.825
we found multiple drugs,

00:18:58.505 --> 00:18:59.945
including this.

00:19:03.345 --> 00:19:04.585
Ketamine.

00:19:04.665 --> 00:19:06.065
It's what you've been tracking, right?

00:19:07.785 --> 00:19:08.825
Yes.

00:19:16.825 --> 00:19:18.425
Sulfuric acid

00:19:18.985 --> 00:19:23.385
and hydrofluoric acid too?

00:19:24.345 --> 00:19:25.265
Why?

00:19:25.345 --> 00:19:29.465
Those are the acids Dr. Tankhun said
were found in Bell's body.

00:19:31.265 --> 00:19:33.665
If Seon Jae sold ketamine,

00:19:33.745 --> 00:19:37.345
the killer probably bought
other chemicals from him too.

00:19:39.625 --> 00:19:41.945
That bastard really was a one-stop shop.

00:19:45.505 --> 00:19:47.505
We only found
Seon Jae's transaction records,

00:19:48.185 --> 00:19:49.705
but no customer list.

00:19:49.785 --> 00:19:51.345
You'll need to dig deeper.

00:19:52.985 --> 00:19:54.865
Then I'll call an emergency meeting.

00:19:56.745 --> 00:19:57.665
Yes.

00:20:05.865 --> 00:20:07.585
Jade hasn't changed at all.

00:20:07.665 --> 00:20:09.185
He's still hot-headed as ever.

00:20:10.065 --> 00:20:12.425
You guys seem pretty close.

00:20:15.185 --> 00:20:18.025
Probably because we trained together
in the Special Investigation Unit.

00:20:21.785 --> 00:20:24.225
I was wondering if you ever…

00:20:25.545 --> 00:20:26.745
You mean, were we dating?

00:20:27.465 --> 00:20:28.865
We are close friends.

00:20:29.385 --> 00:20:30.905
It's just the three of us.

00:20:31.465 --> 00:20:35.665
Lee, Jade, and me.

00:20:36.945 --> 00:20:39.585
But I'm not sure
if Jade still wants to be that close now.

00:20:42.585 --> 00:20:44.585
But our side's cleared things up.

00:20:44.665 --> 00:20:46.025
What about you, Inspector?

00:20:48.905 --> 00:20:50.505
Nothing on our end.

00:20:50.585 --> 00:20:52.905
We're just focusing on the case.

00:20:56.865 --> 00:20:57.945
By the way,

00:20:58.025 --> 00:21:00.585
why did Jade leave
the Special Investigation Unit

00:21:01.465 --> 00:21:03.105
and become a cop alone?

00:21:03.185 --> 00:21:05.625
Jade never told you?

00:21:07.705 --> 00:21:08.785
No.

00:21:10.145 --> 00:21:11.905
He was dismissed before finishing training

00:21:13.625 --> 00:21:14.865
because of me.

00:21:40.105 --> 00:21:42.305
Jade helped me during a test.

00:21:42.385 --> 00:21:46.065
But the coach said
his emotions were a weakness.

00:21:46.945 --> 00:21:47.985
Hey.

00:21:48.065 --> 00:21:49.345
You're dismissed from training.

00:21:50.225 --> 00:21:51.465
Me?

00:21:51.545 --> 00:21:55.705
Anyone who can't separate duty
from emotion is a weakness

00:21:55.785 --> 00:21:57.865
and has no place
in the Special Investigation Unit.

00:21:57.945 --> 00:22:01.505
But I think that's his strength.

00:22:02.665 --> 00:22:06.665
What's the point of all those missions
if you end up with no one left?

00:22:07.785 --> 00:22:08.665
Right?

00:22:13.265 --> 00:22:14.305
Well said.

00:22:19.745 --> 00:22:22.265
We'll excuse ourselves now.

00:22:27.065 --> 00:22:27.905
Well…

00:22:29.665 --> 00:22:31.185
Thank you, Inspector,

00:22:31.945 --> 00:22:34.185
for bringing Jade back to life again.

00:22:36.225 --> 00:22:38.025
Please take care

00:22:38.105 --> 00:22:41.505
of him for us.

00:22:42.825 --> 00:22:43.665
I will.

00:23:05.825 --> 00:23:08.305
The culprit is likely one of these people.

00:23:08.905 --> 00:23:15.065
We suspect they bought ketamine
and body-dissolving acid at The Wild Hunt.

00:23:16.465 --> 00:23:20.425
Lieutenant, look into this further.
Get me more information on it.

00:23:20.505 --> 00:23:21.385
Noted.

00:23:22.105 --> 00:23:23.225
One more thing.

00:23:23.825 --> 00:23:26.585
Question the garage owner.

00:23:26.665 --> 00:23:30.105
I want to know who owns
that white car I saw.

00:23:31.345 --> 00:23:32.945
You're still curious about that car?

00:23:34.945 --> 00:23:35.825
Yes.

00:23:35.905 --> 00:23:37.265
When I went to the garage,

00:23:38.505 --> 00:23:40.465
I saw an engineering jacket
inside the car.

00:23:42.425 --> 00:23:44.025
It has to belong to the Avengers.

00:23:45.185 --> 00:23:46.625
I'll track it down right away.

00:23:46.705 --> 00:23:47.985
Thanks.

00:23:48.585 --> 00:23:52.305
We need to catch the killer
before there's another body.

00:23:53.465 --> 00:23:54.985
Everyone, I'm counting on you.

00:23:56.825 --> 00:23:57.865
Understood.

00:24:07.745 --> 00:24:12.385
{\an8}CLEAN ZONE

00:24:14.745 --> 00:24:15.865
Inspector?

00:24:16.745 --> 00:24:17.905
How is it going?

00:24:18.665 --> 00:24:19.545
Any updates so far?

00:24:19.625 --> 00:24:24.185
Wow, straight to work
the moment you arrive?

00:24:24.985 --> 00:24:26.385
Well, we're colleagues.

00:24:27.265 --> 00:24:28.785
Come on.

00:24:28.865 --> 00:24:30.905
I haven't even eaten yet.

00:24:30.985 --> 00:24:32.825
I'm starving.

00:24:33.585 --> 00:24:35.625
Why don't we grab something good to eat?

00:24:35.705 --> 00:24:40.185
I can also update you while we eat.

00:24:41.505 --> 00:24:45.465
But judging by your face,

00:24:45.545 --> 00:24:46.945
I guess that's a no.

00:24:47.025 --> 00:24:48.585
I'm sorry.

00:24:48.665 --> 00:24:50.385
I'm not used to this.

00:24:50.465 --> 00:24:55.505
When I worked in the States,
I didn't deal with forensics much.

00:24:56.545 --> 00:24:58.665
I see. That's fine.

00:24:58.745 --> 00:25:02.865
Anyway, I reviewed the autopsy.

00:25:03.425 --> 00:25:06.625
Tonkla's body tested positive
for ketamine.

00:25:06.705 --> 00:25:07.745
Ketamine?

00:25:09.265 --> 00:25:10.945
I guess that must be the killer's pattern.

00:25:12.905 --> 00:25:16.065
Both Tar and Bell had it too.

00:25:18.065 --> 00:25:19.465
What I want to know is

00:25:20.105 --> 00:25:22.905
whether the first victim,
Puifai, had it too.

00:25:23.945 --> 00:25:25.505
I'm really sorry, Inspector.

00:25:25.585 --> 00:25:29.305
I didn't request her autopsy report
from the hospital that conducted it.

00:25:30.025 --> 00:25:30.905
I'm really sorry.

00:25:31.585 --> 00:25:32.585
It's okay.

00:25:33.785 --> 00:25:36.025
I'll handle it. Thanks.

00:25:36.785 --> 00:25:38.185
Wait, Inspector.

00:25:39.625 --> 00:25:40.825
Sit down.

00:25:40.905 --> 00:25:42.625
Since Captain Jade isn't here,

00:25:43.265 --> 00:25:44.785
no one can stop me now.

00:25:45.985 --> 00:25:48.145
You really don't want
to have a meal with me?

00:25:49.825 --> 00:25:51.145
I'm sorry.

00:25:52.185 --> 00:25:54.305
I really can't.

00:25:54.905 --> 00:25:56.185
You can't go,

00:25:56.265 --> 00:26:00.065
or is someone stopping you?

00:26:02.905 --> 00:26:08.025
I guess that means I'm out of the running.

00:26:11.985 --> 00:26:16.425
I've never seen Captain Jade
this possessive over anyone before.

00:26:17.985 --> 00:26:19.625
At first, I thought

00:26:19.705 --> 00:26:22.465
he was just teasing me,
blocking me from getting close to you.

00:26:23.185 --> 00:26:25.905
But now, judging by your reaction,

00:26:25.985 --> 00:26:28.425
are you two dating yet?

00:26:31.545 --> 00:26:36.785
Doctor, I'd rather not discuss
personal matters at work.

00:26:38.705 --> 00:26:40.225
That's pretty clear.

00:26:41.185 --> 00:26:44.345
I guess I'll have to withdraw
as a boyfriend candidate.

00:26:47.505 --> 00:26:49.905
If I get evidence from Puifai's case,

00:26:50.505 --> 00:26:52.865
I'll consult you.

00:26:52.945 --> 00:26:54.225
Anytime.

00:26:54.825 --> 00:26:55.665
Thanks.

00:26:55.745 --> 00:26:57.745
But if you ever get your heart broken,

00:26:59.185 --> 00:27:00.585
call me anytime.

00:27:01.385 --> 00:27:02.545
You've got my number.

00:27:10.625 --> 00:27:12.105
I'm going to die single for sure.

00:27:13.025 --> 00:27:15.025
There's no brain damage.

00:27:16.345 --> 00:27:18.745
So he'll be able to remember
everything normally, right?

00:27:19.465 --> 00:27:20.705
That's hard to say.

00:27:20.785 --> 00:27:23.785
But once he recovers physically,

00:27:23.865 --> 00:27:26.505
his memories should gradually return.

00:27:28.625 --> 00:27:29.705
Okay. Thank you very much.

00:27:30.665 --> 00:27:32.305
I'll take my leave now.

00:27:32.385 --> 00:27:33.505
Thank you.

00:27:43.105 --> 00:27:44.945
You don't have to stay and watch me.

00:27:45.025 --> 00:27:46.945
Go back to work. Kamin will scold you.

00:27:47.025 --> 00:27:48.585
You should worry about yourself.

00:27:49.185 --> 00:27:51.825
Being at a crime scene
with a dead body and no answers,

00:27:51.905 --> 00:27:53.745
how long do you think you'll last?

00:27:57.825 --> 00:27:59.825
I'm trying to help you too.

00:27:59.905 --> 00:28:01.265
I don't remember anything.

00:28:02.025 --> 00:28:03.385
I got hit on the head, damn it.

00:28:03.465 --> 00:28:05.145
And if you get targeted at work,

00:28:06.025 --> 00:28:07.905
what are you going to do then?

00:28:08.865 --> 00:28:11.785
Kamin said you're way out of your depth.

00:28:13.865 --> 00:28:16.345
He suspects you less than I do.

00:28:16.425 --> 00:28:17.545
Wait.

00:28:18.145 --> 00:28:19.505
Are you saying you suspect me?

00:28:20.665 --> 00:28:22.465
You think I'm the killer?

00:28:22.545 --> 00:28:24.305
How could you come up with that thought?

00:28:26.385 --> 00:28:28.345
My head hurts even more now, asshole.

00:28:30.585 --> 00:28:33.785
Does Kamin get as annoyed with you
as I do every day?

00:28:34.705 --> 00:28:35.905
What do I do that's annoying?

00:28:36.505 --> 00:28:37.865
I'm a professional.

00:28:38.705 --> 00:28:41.985
I can separate work from personal matters.

00:28:42.065 --> 00:28:43.465
You can separate them?

00:28:44.665 --> 00:28:45.785
Really?

00:28:50.025 --> 00:28:51.505
Well, I can't anymore.

00:28:51.585 --> 00:28:53.305
Work, personal life…

00:28:53.385 --> 00:28:54.345
I'm jealous of him too.

00:28:55.265 --> 00:28:56.625
I can't handle it anymore.

00:29:01.145 --> 00:29:02.865
If he finds out this is who I really am,

00:29:04.185 --> 00:29:06.385
I'll be crossed off again for sure.

00:29:06.985 --> 00:29:09.425
Then why force yourself
to be someone you're not?

00:29:10.145 --> 00:29:12.985
If you can't separate them, then don't.

00:29:14.345 --> 00:29:15.545
Be honest.

00:29:17.145 --> 00:29:19.025
Can you really change who you are?

00:29:19.105 --> 00:29:21.425
Letting your heart lead

00:29:21.505 --> 00:29:22.905
and working with your heart.

00:29:22.985 --> 00:29:25.545
That's one of
the few good things about you.

00:29:26.545 --> 00:29:27.945
It's fine the way it is.

00:29:36.585 --> 00:29:39.505
Don't change.
Or there won't be anything good left.

00:29:40.865 --> 00:29:42.105
You bastard.

00:29:49.705 --> 00:29:51.305
Hello, Dr. Puth.

00:29:51.385 --> 00:29:52.385
This is Kamin,

00:29:52.465 --> 00:29:54.945
the one handling Puifai's case.

00:29:55.025 --> 00:29:56.985
Yes. Please go ahead.

00:29:57.065 --> 00:29:58.225
I have a question.

00:29:58.305 --> 00:30:00.185
During Puifai's autopsy,

00:30:00.265 --> 00:30:02.145
did you find unusual substances?

00:30:02.785 --> 00:30:04.505
Unusual substances?

00:30:05.145 --> 00:30:08.625
Like ketamine.

00:30:16.105 --> 00:30:17.225
Not at first.

00:30:18.265 --> 00:30:19.585
Why do you ask all of a sudden?

00:30:19.665 --> 00:30:24.145
The killer used it
in the murders of the other kids.

00:30:24.225 --> 00:30:27.065
So I was wondering
if Puifai's body had it too.

00:30:27.145 --> 00:30:28.985
Can we run the test again,

00:30:29.065 --> 00:30:32.545
or has the body been released
to the family already?

00:30:32.625 --> 00:30:33.825
Not yet.

00:30:33.905 --> 00:30:35.585
We need to wait until the case is closed.

00:30:35.665 --> 00:30:37.945
The family already held
the ceremony though.

00:30:39.065 --> 00:30:42.345
But I can't guarantee we'll find anything.

00:30:42.425 --> 00:30:43.865
It's been some time.

00:30:44.745 --> 00:30:45.865
I understand.

00:30:45.945 --> 00:30:48.905
Please do what you can.

00:30:48.985 --> 00:30:50.185
Of course.

00:31:04.625 --> 00:31:07.385
Captain, did you go swimming somewhere?

00:31:07.465 --> 00:31:09.225
Swimming? What are you talking about?

00:31:09.305 --> 00:31:10.665
It's raining really hard.

00:31:10.745 --> 00:31:12.505
I rode my motorbike through the rain.

00:31:13.945 --> 00:31:15.065
I'm soaked.

00:31:17.505 --> 00:31:19.305
Hey, what are you doing?

00:31:21.585 --> 00:31:23.025
I'm going to take a shower.

00:31:24.025 --> 00:31:25.545
What are you thinking?

00:31:28.185 --> 00:31:30.025
Can I borrow a towel?

00:31:42.145 --> 00:31:43.065
Here.

00:31:46.225 --> 00:31:47.705
Or do you want to shower with me?

00:31:51.305 --> 00:31:52.705
Just go shower already.

00:32:17.745 --> 00:32:19.425
Take off my shirt you're wearing.

00:32:19.505 --> 00:32:21.105
It looks ridiculous on you.

00:32:22.305 --> 00:32:23.225
Why?

00:32:23.305 --> 00:32:24.625
I think it's cute, Min.

00:32:25.385 --> 00:32:28.945
Also, your shirt smells really nice, Min.

00:32:31.905 --> 00:32:33.585
Call me "Inspector."

00:32:33.665 --> 00:32:35.625
Do you know what time it is?

00:32:36.425 --> 00:32:37.505
It's after work hours.

00:32:38.105 --> 00:32:39.225
I can call you Min.

00:32:41.745 --> 00:32:42.585
Come here.

00:32:56.105 --> 00:32:57.025
Lift your shirt up.

00:32:57.825 --> 00:32:58.665
Hey.

00:33:00.385 --> 00:33:03.385
Are you coming on that strong, Min?

00:33:11.305 --> 00:33:13.105
Min, what are you doing?

00:33:13.705 --> 00:33:15.265
Isn't this what you always imagine?

00:33:16.345 --> 00:33:17.705
Hurry. I need to dress your wound.

00:33:22.105 --> 00:33:23.185
Fine.

00:33:32.105 --> 00:33:32.985
Do it gently, okay?

00:33:37.185 --> 00:33:38.105
Ouch.

00:33:38.185 --> 00:33:39.825
I told you to be gentle.

00:33:48.425 --> 00:33:49.545
You're so rough.

00:33:50.385 --> 00:33:51.505
That's it.

00:33:54.065 --> 00:33:55.625
It hurts like this.

00:33:56.345 --> 00:33:57.705
How am I supposed to put it back on?

00:34:00.585 --> 00:34:01.865
Put it on for me, Min.

00:34:01.945 --> 00:34:03.305
Please.

00:34:03.385 --> 00:34:06.945
I'm hurt.
I don't have the strength to put it on.

00:34:12.784 --> 00:34:13.705
You want me to do it?

00:34:14.425 --> 00:34:15.264
Yes.

00:34:16.185 --> 00:34:17.385
It's hard to put on.

00:34:18.824 --> 00:34:19.665
Okay.

00:34:46.545 --> 00:34:47.385
I'm hungry.

00:34:48.185 --> 00:34:50.105
I'll go make some instant noodles.

00:35:20.345 --> 00:35:21.825
I did what you told me.

00:35:34.985 --> 00:35:35.905
Where are you?

00:35:36.905 --> 00:35:38.185
Come out already!

00:35:38.985 --> 00:35:40.185
Where are you?

00:36:02.585 --> 00:36:04.305
It looks like
it's going to rain all night.

00:36:08.265 --> 00:36:09.385
It should let up soon.

00:36:10.105 --> 00:36:11.505
Then we can go home.

00:36:16.505 --> 00:36:17.785
You know what?

00:36:17.865 --> 00:36:21.425
I'm happy you think of my place as home.

00:36:25.265 --> 00:36:26.745
Well, we signed a contract.

00:36:27.985 --> 00:36:30.745
Also, your place is…

00:36:33.105 --> 00:36:34.665
pretty comfortable to sleep in.

00:36:35.785 --> 00:36:36.825
Really?

00:36:37.505 --> 00:36:39.705
I thought it was comfortable
because I'm there.

00:36:40.425 --> 00:36:42.705
Jeez, you're impossible.
I'm going to throw up.

00:36:42.785 --> 00:36:44.345
Take it down a notch.

00:36:45.425 --> 00:36:47.345
But I mean it.

00:36:48.185 --> 00:36:49.865
It's raining hard.

00:36:49.945 --> 00:36:51.705
Traffic's going to be awful.

00:36:51.785 --> 00:36:53.545
I'm not going out to get stuck in traffic.

00:37:04.065 --> 00:37:05.425
You're right.

00:37:07.665 --> 00:37:09.625
Honestly, you can sleep here.

00:37:09.705 --> 00:37:12.665
If we stay here,
I can keep working on the case.

00:37:12.745 --> 00:37:13.825
No.

00:37:14.585 --> 00:37:16.145
Off work means off work.

00:37:16.225 --> 00:37:18.945
You've been working hard.
You need to rest.

00:37:22.545 --> 00:37:23.505
Wait a second.

00:37:31.585 --> 00:37:32.465
Hey?

00:37:32.545 --> 00:37:35.065
Whoa, do you have everything?

00:37:35.985 --> 00:37:38.025
It's called being prepared.

00:37:47.585 --> 00:37:48.465
Go to sleep,

00:37:49.505 --> 00:37:51.385
so you can wake up
and do the job you love.

00:38:08.625 --> 00:38:09.745
Sleeping like this,

00:38:10.265 --> 00:38:11.265
won't it hurt your wound?

00:38:12.905 --> 00:38:15.145
This? Not at all.

00:38:16.745 --> 00:38:19.505
I can handle
much more challenging positions.

00:38:21.945 --> 00:38:23.025
Pervert.

00:38:25.225 --> 00:38:27.505
Did Dr. Tankhun flirt with you today?

00:38:32.665 --> 00:38:35.145
But I've made it clear to him.
I'm trustworthy.

00:38:36.785 --> 00:38:39.385
You're the only one who won't back off.

00:38:40.785 --> 00:38:42.545
Why would I back off?

00:38:42.625 --> 00:38:44.425
Dream on. I won't give in.

00:38:45.465 --> 00:38:49.825
I'm going to slowly move closer to you

00:38:51.625 --> 00:38:53.465
and knock on your door.

00:38:54.065 --> 00:38:55.505
You can knock,

00:38:56.505 --> 00:38:57.425
but you can't open it.

00:38:59.505 --> 00:39:00.625
I threw away the key.

00:39:01.185 --> 00:39:02.305
Really?

00:39:05.225 --> 00:39:06.385
What about you?

00:39:07.545 --> 00:39:11.345
Have you come to terms with
leaving the Special Investigation Unit?

00:39:14.865 --> 00:39:16.145
How do you know about that?

00:39:18.145 --> 00:39:19.385
Did you ask Yuki?

00:39:20.945 --> 00:39:21.865
Yeah.

00:39:23.505 --> 00:39:24.985
That was a long time ago.

00:39:25.585 --> 00:39:27.225
I've moved on.

00:39:28.305 --> 00:39:32.225
Right now, I'm more focused on
the person in front of me.

00:39:36.145 --> 00:39:38.065
When we went into The Wild Hunt,

00:39:40.385 --> 00:39:41.545
it was so obvious.

00:39:43.145 --> 00:39:44.425
How so?

00:39:48.225 --> 00:39:49.705
When I went inside,

00:39:52.185 --> 00:39:53.585
all I could think about was you.

00:39:55.705 --> 00:39:57.305
I was only worried about you.

00:40:00.465 --> 00:40:01.585
That much?

00:40:02.385 --> 00:40:03.225
Yeah.

00:40:05.865 --> 00:40:07.025
What?

00:40:07.785 --> 00:40:08.865
What about you?

00:40:28.385 --> 00:40:30.265
I was only worried about you too, Jade.

00:40:38.745 --> 00:40:39.825
Are we…

00:40:42.785 --> 00:40:45.105
more than just boss and subordinate now?

00:40:54.065 --> 00:40:55.025
It's been that way for a long time.

00:40:57.305 --> 00:40:59.065
You're the only one who didn't notice.

00:42:05.825 --> 00:42:07.265
The real letter is with us.

00:42:08.345 --> 00:42:10.385
The killer left a fake one here.

00:42:10.465 --> 00:42:12.105
What a blatant provocation.

00:42:22.865 --> 00:42:24.665
What if one day
you or I receive the letter?

00:42:24.745 --> 00:42:26.265
I'll protect you.

00:42:29.145 --> 00:42:30.185
No need.

00:42:31.545 --> 00:42:34.065
We have to compete
to catch the serial killer.

00:42:36.145 --> 00:42:36.985
Yes.

00:42:38.185 --> 00:42:39.225
But while we work,

00:42:39.785 --> 00:42:41.185
I'll do everything I can

00:42:41.785 --> 00:42:43.425
to make sure you're safe.

00:42:44.825 --> 00:42:49.025
And I'm not doing this out of duty.

00:42:53.265 --> 00:42:54.745
You can protect yourself.

00:42:55.785 --> 00:42:58.545
But I'll protect you myself.

00:43:20.945 --> 00:43:22.545
Have you and Cherreen
received the letter yet?

00:43:22.625 --> 00:43:23.785
Don't worry about us.

00:43:23.865 --> 00:43:25.585
You should spend your time guarding Jay.

00:43:25.665 --> 00:43:27.265
Don't worry about what Champ said.

00:43:27.345 --> 00:43:29.345
I won't let anything worse happen to Jay.

00:43:31.505 --> 00:43:32.745
We've received the letter.

00:43:32.825 --> 00:43:34.025
Check on Jay at the hospital.

00:43:34.105 --> 00:43:35.945
Let Lieutenant Prai and Lieutenant Ken
handle this minor task.

00:43:36.025 --> 00:43:37.345
I said go, so go!

00:43:38.825 --> 00:43:41.385
Just because I pursued you first
doesn't mean you can do whatever you want.

00:43:41.465 --> 00:43:43.185
- I was just--
- Just what?

00:43:44.945 --> 00:43:46.465
Even if I'm not a good person,

00:43:47.225 --> 00:43:48.625
please let me love you.